# Templates — Ticketing API

Replace `[Feature]`, `[Action]`, `[Area]`, `[TId]`.  
Source patterns adapted from Elay CQRS habits; HTTP/status follow Ticket OpenAPI.

---

## 1. Domain entity

```csharp
namespace Ticket.Domain.Entities;

/// <summary>Represents [business concept].</summary>
public sealed class [Feature]
{
    public [TId] Id { get; set; }
    public required string Name { get; set; }
    public bool IsActive { get; set; } = true;
    public bool IsDeleted { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; } = DateTime.UtcNow;

    public static [Feature] Create(string name)
    {
        ArgumentException.ThrowIfNullOrWhiteSpace(name);
        return new [Feature] { Name = name.Trim(), IsActive = true };
    }
}
```

Do not hard-delete; deactivate / set `IsDeleted` per DESIGN.

