## 2. DTOs

```csharp
namespace Ticket.Application.DTOs;

/// <summary>API response shape for [Feature] (camelCase in JSON).</summary>
public sealed record [Feature]Dto(int Id, string Name, bool IsActive);

/// <summary>Input for create/update.</summary>
public sealed record [Feature]Model(string Name, bool IsActive = true);
```

Match `openapi.json` field names exactly.

