## 3. Feature errors

```csharp
namespace Ticket.Application.Errors;

public static class [Feature]Errors
{
    public static Error NotFound => Error.NotFound("[Feature].NotFound", "[Feature] was not found");
    public static Error Conflict => Error.Conflict("[Feature].Conflict", "Conflict while updating [Feature]");
}
```

Map `Error` types to ProblemDetails status codes in the API pipeline (404/409/…).

