## 4. Command + validator (same file)

```csharp
namespace Ticket.Application.Features.[Feature].Commands;

public sealed record [Action][Feature]Command([Feature]Model Model) : IRequest<Result<[TResponse]>>;

public sealed class [Action][Feature]CommandValidator : AbstractValidator<[Action][Feature]Command>
{
    public [Action][Feature]CommandValidator()
    {
        RuleFor(x => x.Model.Name).NotEmpty().MinimumLength(2).MaximumLength(200);
    }
}
```

